## 🔧 Week 9: Enhanced Implementation

This week focused on turning the SecureHome VPN project from a basic simulation into a fully functional platform.

### ✅ Enhancements Made:
- Integrated real **WireGuard** VPN backend using `wg show` to reflect live connection status
- Implemented **VPN Connect/Disconnect** logic with accurate green/red status bar
- Replaced fake “Live Connection” box with real-time VPN status indicators
- Integrated **RustDesk** remote desktop launcher for full video/voice simulation
- Fixed and re-enabled the **Dark Mode toggle** with cookie-based persistence
- Restored **smart reminder form** with flash confirmation
- Moved VPN logs to a dedicated page with timestamps
- Added **server selection dropdown** logic
- Improved the login screen layout (centered and styled)

